name: Arbitrum Token
reason:
This PR invalidates #PR125 and replaces it with a better logo. 

Arbitrum Foundation finally rolled out a token (https://twitter.com/arbitrum/status/1636362096714690562?s=20). For this, I think it makes sense to have it ready for launch so that users can seamlessly trade the token without having to import it. From the documentation, I have been able to find that this is all the info relating the token:

https://docs.arbitrum.foundation/airdrop-eligibility-distribution
https://docs.arbitrum.foundation/deployment-addresses
https://etherscan.io/token/0xB50721BCf8d664c30412Cfbc6cf7a15145234ad1
